content: I think I'll go with the warm flour tortillas for this one. I'm really craving that taco-like feel. And speaking of cravings, I've been meaning to ask, do you have any recipes for chicken tortilla soup? My coworker taught me how to make it last month, and it's been a game-changer for my lunch routine. I've made it like 4 times since then, and it's just so comforting and delicious.
